AuroraOS assembles free/open-source software (Debian, GNOME, Tor, the Linux
kernel, and others) using Debian's live-build. Each of those components retains
its own license; this MIT license covers only the AuroraOS-specific build
configuration, scripts, website, and tooling in this repository.

AuroraOS is not affiliated with the Tor Project or with Tails. For genuine
high-stakes anonymity, use Tails: https://tails.net
